person.persName: Frederick A. Frische (Jefferson County, Kentucky, notary public)

body.p: Jefferson County, Kentucky, clerk and notary public. Kentucky native. Son of Frederick Frische and Elizabeth Frische. Clerk in Jefferson County in 1860. Notary Public in Jefferson County in 1861.
